<!--mainpage area begins here--><h2 class="head">CO1003 Worksheet 3</h2>
    <p>
      You should not start this worksheet until you have finished
      <a href="wksheet2" target="another" shape="rect">Worksheet 2</a> and
      uploaded the solutions in JACK. 
    </p> 

    
      <h3 class="head"><a name="section-1">Introduction</a></h3>

      
      <p>
	This worksheet introduces you to some additional object-oriented
	concepts. There are two exercises.
     </p>
      
      The exercises should be submitted by 11:59pm, Wednesday
	    29 October, 2014.

      <h3 class="head"><a name="section-1">Coversheets</a></h3>
 	<table><tr><td style="background-color:yellow" rowspan="1" colspan="1">
