      <hr>
      <p>
	Using the instructions on this webpage, 
	<a href="https://jack-leic.s3.uni-due.de/jack2/home.jsf" target="_blank" shape="rect">log into JACK</a>
	and do the exercises for Worksheet 3.
      </p>

